---
layout: default
title: GitHub Repositories Plugin for Eleventy
---

This page displays all of the repositories for the configured GitHub user account using the <a href="https://github.com/johnwargo/eleventy-plugin-github-repos" target="_blank">Eleventy Plugin GitHub Repositories</a> plugin.

{% if collections.githubRepos.length > 0 %}
  <p>Number of Repositories: {{ collections.githubRepos.length }}</p>
  <ul>
  {% for repo in collections.githubRepos %}
    <li>   
      <a href="{{ repo.html_url }}" target="_blank">{{ repo.name }}</a>
      {% if repo.description.length > 0 %}
        {{ repo.description }}
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>  
{% else %}
  <p>No repository data to display</p>
{% endif %}
